<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="True-bred" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">True-bred,</orth> of a right breed, genuine: <cit><quote>she's a beagle, t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.195" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 195</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>t. cowards,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.206" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 206</bibl></cit>. <emph>a'</emph> (the knave) <cit><quote>will not out; he is t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.3.71" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 3, 71</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O, t.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.247" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 247</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>